Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bummers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even see in front me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when it'll stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain like this for at least another hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You a merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got food, sell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The long rain ruined everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is empty... and I'm not a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what're you planning to put inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a huge jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, mister... a corpse... A corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a journey to bring home a rainbow in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell us why you're doing such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use something to cure the boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenro! Stop your pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, not again?! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the rain is coming... the rain is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A rainbow will appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I could remember, my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,would suddenly become a different person when he sensed a coming rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He would run about so happily\N in the fields and mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and not come back home for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was strange like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, several days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,someone had find him stuck in the mud,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or he'd just pop in at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And... on those days when it didn't rain, \Nhe would drink enough water to shower in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you how embarrassing this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be better if you never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know myself what's happened to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From the time I saw that rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost your mind... that's all it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fun when you run around in the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it's fun beyond description...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma will yell at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me again about the rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep this a secret from Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That day was the day before you were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The flood waters finally retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... after all the work we did building it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably means we didn't \Nthink it through hard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think we could build\N a bridge stronger than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A rainbow... It's so vivid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that when he looked more closely,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the rainbow was growing out of\N the riverbank right nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say if you dig at the foot\N of a rainbow, you'll find treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It disapp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, the rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,began appearing somewhere after every rainfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It changed it's form every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It entertained Pa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but the others apparently couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who showed any reaction was me, though I was still an infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But then one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the rainbow seemed so far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, it never appeared again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel parched no matter how much water I drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My body becomes restless from deep inside
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,on days when it looks like it's gonna rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing I know I'm running\N about the hills and plains...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And in these moments of sanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I long... so long for that rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The whereabouts of that rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go and find it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But soon, Pa became bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even then, he'd struggle to go\N outside before every rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he became too weak to even stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pa, your water...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see that rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am on a journey to, somehow or other, find that rainbow and show it to Pa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you plan to grab the rainbow with both hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't know until I actually see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's down to a drizzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll be on my way now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your story had a weak ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to look for that rainbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you should go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't just a tall story, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What your father saw is a mushi called {\i1}Kouda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\bord2.5\fad(50,50)\pos(640,30.667)\i1}Note:- Kou = rainbow; da = snake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only seen it once before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see its base rooted to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you'd like, I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My compensation, you pay for my meals during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and about that big jar, sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll be of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,normal rainbows can only be seen\N with the sun at your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.67,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\frz23.51\move(884,34,884,182,25,4195)\c&H13171B&\3c&H13171B&}Rainbow \NSnake
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kouda appear regardless of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The order of the colors is reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't check that first, \Nyou'll be chasing rainbows forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you said your name was Ginko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have some reason to be traveling, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why help a passerby like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I want to see it, too. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not traveling for any special purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't be searching for {\i1}Kouda{\i0} forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's see... if we don't find it by the first day of autumn, I'll quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, like rainbows,\N it appears often after the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to move about by reading the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned quite a bit about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any rain around here for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... there are clouds around that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain in that area tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't just been walking aimlessly about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's an ordinary rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I expected this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look for something, you don't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since you began your journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that story about showing it\N to your bedridden father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a lie, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would travel five years with sick family at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to show it to Pa wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But that isn't what got me started on my quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I tell you my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Koro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\bord2.5\fad(50,50)\pos(640,30.667)\i1}Note:- Ko = rainbow; Ro = man
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a name that always reminds people of my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who wandered about in search of rainbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my name, I was \Nthe laughingstock of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In a western province, there is a famous rogue river.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from a long line of bridge builders who built the bridge that spanned that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times we rebuilt it, \Nfloods washed the bridge away each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone had high hopes for Pa, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My older brother, who followed in Pa's footsteps, was very talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time it was destroyed, \Nhe designed a more solid bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have an ounce of his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After tearing a tendon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost the full use of my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worse than second-rate as a carpenter as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, the only \Nplace for me was at Pa's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand it, so I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, after all that, what {\i1}is{\i0} your reason for searching for the rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time I saw a rainbow, I couldn't keep myself from chasing after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to confirm what Pa said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to say to the people\N who laughed at Pa and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"This was the cause."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though I left the village, I'm still a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed some sort of goal in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't go on living just for living's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A goal, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were traveling without a purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,well... I suppose you have your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Traveling about is not an easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can a person keep on traveling \Nabout without a purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes I do want to take a rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I feel that way, I set a goal like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that creates some leisure time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who "live for living's sake"\N have no leisure time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very serious about what I'm doing... but for you it's a diversion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} taking this very seriously, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an issue of attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Relaxing is one of life's pressing issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, I think it is a more \Nhonest motivation than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All you're doing is torturing yourself by chasing after rainbows to ease your guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've set roots anywhere\N and discarded your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't... that's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe it's time to put an end to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll quit after the first day of autumn, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have a good eye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are mermaid's nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They make a love potion when \Nboiled in water and drunk as tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have some medicine that'll bring rain, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With the long drought that we've been having...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the rice fields will dry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was such a medicine, I'd have used it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep a sharp eye on the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time it rained?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My throat's parched...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't even perspire any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rain is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rain is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rain is coming... the rain is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A rainbow will appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.02,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The sun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...inside the rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about my love potion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm closing shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't run so fast from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd it disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The location should be about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This area looks like it might still rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not have gone very far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew where the rain would be without seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it like this for Pa, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Koro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably at the point
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,where you come to detest me \Nand the name I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give you the name \Nof the most beautiful thing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I had ever seen in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, your friends laugh at you, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought up a different, better name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,From tomorrow, use this name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say... such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not... going to give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become an even better...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...bridge builder than you, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! It's close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:47.78,Alt,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The name of the most beautiful thing I had ever seen in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't'!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What Pa said was true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to bring this home with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no proof until I saw it up-close...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I felt a shock on my skin when I touched...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one type of {\i1}nagaremono.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\bord2.5\fad(50,50)\pos(640,30.667)\i1}Note:- nagare = flow, mono = thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nagaremono?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They possess life, but they\N resemble natural phenomena...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for the fact that they are alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they're identical to rainbows, a \Nphenomena created by light and rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Kouda{\i0} was likely the result of light and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-laden rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kouki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the basis of mushi life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nagaremono{\i0} are things that \Nresemble floods and typhoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They happen for a reason, but they have no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They are born only to drift...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not affected by {\i1}anything;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,they only affect other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be possessed when you touch such a mushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For an instant, I felt as though I was within it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if Pa was swallowed up by that rising, waterfall-like object?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it wasn't something I could have my way with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a part of me is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's rather refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you going to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? I'll think about it a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're like this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just start drifting again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, I have no idea where that man went.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I did hear that an indestructible\N bridge had been built
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}across the famous rogue river in a western province.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the water rises, \None side of each plank is detached
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and allowed to flow with the waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the waters recede, the bridge is restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Nagare-bashi, as it is called, was built from the ideas of one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:35.64,Next Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(833,560)\fad(0,2000)\be1}Raindrops and Rainbows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.98,Next Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,416)\fad(2000,0)\be1\c&H5A5D5B&}Where\NSea\NMeets\NMan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where Sea Meets Man.
